March 29, 2018 / 5:56 PM / in 5 minutes BRIEF-Keybank To Sell Key Insurance & Benefits Services Reuters Staff 
* KEYBANK ENTERS INTO AGREEMENT TO SELL KEY INSURANCE & BENEFITS SERVICES, INC. TO USI INSURANCE SERVICES 
* KEYCORP - TRANSACTION EXPECTED TO CLOSE IN Q2 2018 
* KEYCORP - KEYBANK ACQUIRED KEY INSURANCE & BENEFITS SERVICES, INC. AS PART OF 2016 MERGER WITH FIRST NIAGARA FINANCIAL Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
